author: Christian Heimes
commit_message:
Rename C extension module from _sha3 to _pysha3

_sha3 conflicts with the extension module from Python 3.6. On Linux the
_sha3 extension module is compiled as shared library and can be
shadowed. On Windows (and apparently macOS) it's builtin.

Closes: #4
Signed-off-by: Christian Heimes <christian@python.org>
